* A. Banyaga, ''On fixed points of symplectic maps'', [[Inventiones Mathematicae]] 56 (1980), no. 3, 215&ndash;229.  {{MR|0561971}}
* A. Banyaga, ''On Isomorphic Classical Diffeomorphism Groups. I.'',  [[Proceedings of the American Mathematical Society]] 98 (1986), no. 1, 113&ndash;118.  {{JSTOR|2045779}} {{MR|0848887}}
* A. Banyaga, ''On Isomorphic Classical Diffeomorphism Groups. II.'',  [[Journal of Differential Geometry]]  28 (1988), no. 1, 23&ndash;35. {{MR|0950553}}
* A. Banyaga, ''A note on [[Alan Weinstein|Weinstein]]'s conjecture'', Proceedings of the American Mathematical Society 123 ), no. 12, 3901&ndash;3906.  {{JSTOR|2048230}} {{MR|1021206}}

